        "text": "47",
        "rationale": "You added the legs instead of using a²+b²=c²."
      }
    ],
    "correct_choice": "B",
    "explanation": "By the Pythagorean theorem, c² = 12² + 35² = 144 + 1225 = 1369, so c = 37.",
    "estimated_time_seconds": 85,
